	<Title>
		Salt craving: A symptom of Addison&apos;s disease?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Excessive salt craving may indicate an underlying medical condition such as Addison&apos;s disease.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		My husband constantly craves salt. What causes this?
	</Question>
